steps.name: I skip linking my card
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I mock the location of the device to "DENMARK_10888"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Profile" tab is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "DENMARK_10888" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "DENMARK_10888" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "CAR WASH" tab is displayed
I click on "CAR WASH" tab
I make sure that the "CAR WASH" tab is in the default state
I click on Car Wash "CHECK PROGRAMS" button
I check that the "CW Payment Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "CLASSIC SÆSON" Car Wash plan PRICE_NORMAL element
I click on "SELECT WASH" button of "CLASSIC SÆSON" Car Wash
I check that the "Confirm Your Wash Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "CURRENT CW" text
I check that the application text: "CLASSIC SÆSON" is equals to expected value: "CLASSIC SÆSON"
I swipe on the device screen to the "DOWN"
I accept Updated Terms and Conditions
I click on "STAY IN THE CAR" plan radio button
I click on "CONTINUE TO PAYMENT" button
I swipe on the device screen to the "DOWN"
I check that the "CONTINUE TO PAYMENT" button is not displayed
I check that the "Start Your Wash Screen" is displayed
I wait until the "WASH BAY" is available again
I click on "ENTER WASH BAY" button
I check "ENTER WASH BAY" button is not displayed
I check if the progress bar on the "CAR WASH" tab is advancing
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I click on "TRANSACTION HISTORY" button
I check that the "Activity History Screen" is displayed
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane" on Activity History page
I check if new transaction appears on the "ACTIVITY HISTORY" list within 10 seconds
